  "texts": [
    "Compliance with regulatory frameworks such as the GDPR and HIPAA is necessary to uphold ethical standards in AI deployment.",
    "However, despite these innovations, data breaches and adversarial vulnerabilities persist.",
    "Aldoseri et al.",
    "(113) emphasize the need for domain-specific data protection strategies tailored to the unique risks posed by dietary and health datasets.",
    "Moving forward, the development of user-centric privacy frameworks that promote transparency and informed consent will be crucial."
  ]
